"GL2454RT-NM0-B10 VER:T1.0" is silkscreened on the board.
FCC internal photos show the device with a SST39VF800A-90-4C-EK (1MB). The DD-WRT wiki states the device has 2MB RAM.. and the device pictured in this entry has a 2MB Flash chip.
